examples.en: ...diamonds are widely considered to be indestructible because they are one of the hardest known substances...
Water and milk are liquid substances.
This product contains no artificial colors  only natural substances are used.
The immune response recognizes invading substances.

The law prohibits the burial of toxic substances without special permits.
A lot of painkillers have turned out to be addictive substances for patients.
The presence of certain substances in the blood can cause the arteries to harden.
